saction history to compare against, but absence of history alone does not imply fraud risk. Given the low risk score, the recommended action is to process the transaction and send a standard SMS alert to the customer to verify the transaction. No immediate blocking or additional authentication challenges are recommended.", "agent": "SentinelAgent"}, "request_id": null}
